# Title: DotNET Assembly DLL Loaded Via Office Application
# Author: Antonlovesdnb
# Date: 2020-02-19
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects any assembly DLL being loaded by an Office Product
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1204.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_office_dotnet_assembly_dll_load.yml

ImageLoaded="C:\\Windows\\assembly\\*" Image IN ("*\\excel.exe", "*\\mspub.exe", "*\\onenote.exe", "*\\onenoteim.exe", "*\\outlook.exe", "*\\powerpnt.exe", "*\\winword.exe")